mvn clean install

docker build -t javaexpress/user-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/product-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/shipping-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/payment-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/favourite-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/order-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/eurekaserver-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/audit-service:latest .

docker build -t javaexpress/apigateway-service:latest .

Push Images to Docker Hub
-------------------------
docker login
	username
	password

docker push javaexpress/user-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/product-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/shipping-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/payment-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/order-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/favourite-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/eurekaserver-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/audit-service:latest
docker push javaexpress/apigateway-service:latest

Pull Docker Images into your local
-----------------------------------
docker pull javaexpress/user-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/product-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/shipping-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/payment-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/order-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/favourite-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/eurekaserver-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/audit-service:latest
docker pull javaexpress/apigateway-service:latest


